                <h2>About ReadRecall</h2>
                <p class="w-75">
                    Welcome to ReadRecall, your personalized book notes and reading tracker! ReadRecall is a capstone project inspired by the idea of efficiently managing and recalling information from the non-fiction books you read. The project draws inspiration from Derek Sivers' book notes and ratings website, offering a similar space for you to organize your reading journey.
                </p>
